  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"id-1.20.2-Improvements\">Improvements</h3><ul><li><p>Bluefin Integration now allows debit transactions. Depending on the card type, customers can now choose whether to pay with debit or credit networks.</p></li><li><p>Improvements to Integrated Payments, reducing duplicate transactions with identical Transaction IDs on the same ticket.</p></li><li><p>Improvements to tax-inclusive pricing for GST compliance.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.20.2-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Appointment concurrency settings no longer conflict with closed appointments.</p></li><li><p>Activating availability windows will not interfere with appointment visibility in the list view.</p></li><li><p>Optimized reporting to generate results when selecting more than 150 locations.</p></li><li><p>Tip transaction details are no longer hidden after generating a Reconciliation Report.</p></li><li><p>Tip refund logic has been fixed when selecting &quot;Refund Tip Amount First&quot;.</p></li><li><p>Integrated transactions without a tip will no longer appear on the Tip Report.</p></li><li><p>Integrated partial payments no longer incorrectly show as the full amount paid on a ticket.</p></li><li><p>Existing quantities on a Purchase Order are now unaffected after using the Quick Create feature while creating the PO.</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
